wiki.content: The title song God's Menu is characterized by strong addictiveness that you will never forget once you hear it. In the title, the existing meaning of a new menu and the meaning of God are doubled. The eight members refer to the new song as a dish, that contains the ambition to capture the taste and taste of all listeners with this menu. Bang Chan, Changbin and Han who wrote and composed this song, said "It is a song that adds various instruments to an intense hip-hop sound. Stray Kids' slogan STEP OUT,'I will break the existing frame and take a new step ahead, I tried to emphasize the meaning. The performance is also an experimental feeling that I have never seen before." Stray Kids devoted their enthusiasm and passion to realize 100% of the group's natural charm by guiding the entire album's keywords, concepts, and music. Using raw rough eyes and gorgeous graffiti effects, the vivid feeling of living and breathing is expressed visually. In particular, the members suggested the collaboration with the musician who watched with interest in order to realize the color of the team well.
